      • switchDirection

        private void switchDirection(SnakeDirection nextDirection)
        Changes the current direction of the snake. If next direction is the same as or opposite of the current direction the method returns without making changes.
        Parameters:
        nextDirection - The desired direction of the snake.

      • reverseMovement

        private void reverseMovement()
        Reverses the movement of the snake.

      • moveSnake

        private void moveSnake()
        Moves the snake with 1 tile. The method also checks the type of the next tile and takes action accordingly.
        • If direction is Up - next tile is [x-1][y];
        • if direction is Down - next tile is [x+1][y];
        • if direction is Left - next tile is [x][y-1];
        • if direction is Right - next tile is [x][y+1];

      • changeTileType

        private void changeTileType(Tile tile,
                            TileType newType)
        Changes the tile type of the given tile. The GUI is updated afterwards.
        Parameters:
        tile - The tile to get updated.
        newType - The new tile type.
